15 imprisonment in the custody of the Department of Corrections for not
16 more than four (4) years, or by a fine not exceeding Five Thousand
17 Dollars ($5,000.00), or by both such fine and imprisonment. The
18 provisions of Section 51.1 of this title shall apply to any second
19 or subsequent offense.
